consequences.

10:30.997 --> 10:36.035 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Hari Sreenivasan joins us from
our New York
studio tonight with a look at
the latest concerns

10:36.069 --> 10:38.938 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
in the beginning of a periodic
series on the
subject.

10:38.972 --> 10:43.943 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Viral
conspiracy theories
masquerading as news spread at
incredible

10:43.977 --> 10:48.681 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
speeds throughout the election
cycle across
social platforms like Facebook,
Reddit, Twitter

10:48.715 --> 10:55.054 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
and 4chan, but on December 4
came a very real
measure of their impact.

10:55.088 --> 10:59.926 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
A 28-year-old man from North
Carolina man
entered Comet Ping Pong pizza in
Washington,

10:59.959 --> 11:04.364 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
D.C., armed with an assault
rifle, claiming
he wanted to -- quote --
"self-investigate"

11:04.397 --> 11:06.666 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
a fast-spreading theory.

11:06.699 --> 11:12.171 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Edgar Maddison Welch, seen here
with his arms
up, was intrigued by the totally
false conspiracy

11:12.205 --> 11:17.544 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
theory that the pizzeria was
part of a child
abuse ring led by Hillary
Clinton and her

11:17.577 --> 11:19.612 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
