11:19.646 --> 11:23.783 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
After aiming at an employee and
discharging
a weapon, he surrendered to
authorities.

11:23.816 --> 11:26.986 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Luckily, everyone inside escaped
unharmed.

11:27.020 --> 11:31.524 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
This week, more fallout from
what has been
dubbed as Pizzagate: The Trump
transition

11:31.558 --> 11:36.095 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
team removed Michael Flynn Jr.,
the son of
the man president-elect Trump
wants as his

11:36.129 --> 11:41.834 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
national security adviser, after
it became
clear that Flynn Jr. was
retweeting this and

11:41.868 --> 11:44.470 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
other conspiracies.

11:44.504 --> 11:49.042 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Hillary Clinton, herself the
target of other
lies spread over the Web
repeatedly, weighed

11:49.075 --> 11:51.811 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
in during one of her few public
appearances
since the election.

11:51.844 --> 11:55.281 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HILLARY RODHAM CLINTON, Former
U.S. Secretary
of State: It's now clear that
so-called fake

11:55.315 --> 11:59.052 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
news can have real-world
consequences.

11:59.085 --> 12:02.922 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
This isn't about politics or
partisanship.

12:02.956 --> 12:07.660 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Lives are at risk, lives of
ordinary people
just trying to go about their
days, to do

12:07.694 --> 12:10.563 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
their jobs, contribute to their
communities.

12:10.597 --> 12:14.734 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Technology
companies like
Facebook and Google say they are
working to

12:14.767 --> 12:17.904 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
tackle the proliferation of fake
news.

12:17.937 --> 12:22.609 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
One way has been to decrease the
incentives
for advertising that appears on
