12:22.642 --> 12:25.878 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Sheryl Sandberg, the COO of
Facebook, on Thursday's
"Today Show":

12:25.912 --> 12:29.215 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SHERYL SANDBERG, COO, Facebook:
We have taken
important steps, but there is a
lot more to

12:29.248 --> 12:31.017 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
do.

12:31.050 --> 12:33.586 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We know that people don't want
to see hoaxes
on Facebook and we don't want to
see hoaxes

12:33.620 --> 12:35.321 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
on Facebook.

12:35.355 --> 12:38.458 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: According to a
BuzzFeed
News investigation, many fake
news sites are

12:38.491 --> 12:44.163 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
built purely for profit,
